          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "\"In early March, my child... had a cough,” a parent wrote. “Her high school requested that I take my daughter to the doctor for COVID19 testing before she could fully return to school activities. In reliance on the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
